descriptionHtml:
============Solitude Military Ward============

Creates a new area in Solitude, accessible by door. Its sort of created as a dungeon for a Stormcloak soldier, or just to give Solitude a bit more of a loreish feeling.


NOTE: Any custom armour seen in the images are not from this mod, the custom armours are from another imperial mod. This mod ONLY includes the locations seen.

=================
Update to mod
=================

None atm.

=================
Finished Armours
=================
Finished areas:

Solitude Foundry
Imperial Military Headquarters

=================
Whats been done:
=================
I have added two interior cells, not fully navmeshed YET.
Out door area with soldiers as well as loot.

=================
Future Plans:
=================

Barracks
Stables
Kitchen


=================
Installation:
=================
Drag esp. into your \"data\" file in your Skyrim directory.


=================
To Remove:
=================
1. Delete the ESP.


Enjoy the mods ! Please leave feedback!

//CelsiuZ
